1
00:00:06,980 --> 00:00:10,100
♪I love the clarity in your eyes♪

2
00:00:10,740 --> 00:00:13,860
♪Like a shooting star across my world♪

3
00:00:14,500 --> 00:00:17,580
♪Repeating the goodbye we never said♪

4
00:00:18,260 --> 00:00:21,540
♪Through sleepless nights♪

5
00:00:21,980 --> 00:00:25,100
♪I miss the way you looked at me♪

6
00:00:25,700 --> 00:00:30,260
♪Like photos freezing that summer bit by bit♪

7
00:00:30,660 --> 00:00:35,380
♪By the shore with warm winds, maybe we'll meet again♪

8
00:00:37,380 --> 00:00:41,460
[Fall in Love Again]

9
00:00:41,460 --> 00:00:43,980
[Episode 18]

10
00:00:45,520 --> 00:00:46,600
What's going on?

11
00:00:49,160 --> 00:00:52,360
I've actually wanted to tell you for a while.

12
00:00:52,760 --> 00:00:53,760
I just never found the right moment.

13
00:00:53,760 --> 00:00:54,520
Stop.

14
00:00:55,680 --> 00:00:58,960
Are you serious about him?

15
00:01:02,680 --> 00:01:05,200
You know Mr. Song's into you, right?

16
00:01:05,360 --> 00:01:06,440
Mr. Song?

17
00:01:06,440 --> 00:01:08,200
I told you ages ago, it's never happening.

18
00:01:08,560 --> 00:01:09,520
You don't feel that way about him?

19
00:01:09,760 --> 00:01:11,960
What I feel is family, nothing more.

20
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:13,880
- Then what you have with him is love? - Stop saying.

21
00:01:16,560 --> 00:01:19,000
It's hot. Yang, grab some melon.

22
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:22,200
Watermelon.

23
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:27,400
This time, it's real drama.

24
00:01:31,320 --> 00:01:32,680
As for you two,

25
00:01:32,960 --> 00:01:34,480
you have my blessing.

26
00:01:35,040 --> 00:01:36,600
But I have one condition.

27
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:38,400
Until "Have Fun" airs,

28
00:01:38,400 --> 00:01:39,800
no going public. Can you do that?

29
00:01:39,800 --> 00:01:40,640
- No problem. - No problem.

30
00:01:45,320 --> 00:01:46,120
Watermelon.

31
00:01:50,580 --> 00:01:57,140
[Congrats on wrapping "Have Fun"]

32
00:01:57,360 --> 00:01:59,280
Cut. That's a wrap!

33
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:01,960
- Great! - Congrats on the wrap!

34
00:02:02,320 --> 00:02:03,520
- Happy wrap day! - Happy wrap!

35
00:02:04,080 --> 00:02:05,600
Congrats!

36
00:02:05,720 --> 00:02:06,600
Thanks for all the hard work.

37
00:02:06,600 --> 00:02:08,320
- Great job. - Thank you.

38
00:02:08,320 --> 00:02:08,910
Jingxi,

39
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:10,030
happy wrap.

40
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:11,240
Thanks, Xiwen.

41
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:12,680
- Thanks, everyone. - Thank you, Director.

42
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:14,280
Thanks, Director.

43
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,200
Great work.

44
00:02:18,560 --> 00:02:19,360
Thanks for the hard work.

45
00:02:19,640 --> 00:02:21,840
- Great work. - Thank you.

46
00:02:26,040 --> 00:02:27,040
Everyone, quiet for a moment.

47
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:30,560
Today is definitely worth celebrating.

48
00:02:31,160 --> 00:02:34,400
We've officially wrapped "Have Fun".

49
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:37,560
Thank you to every cast and crew member.

50
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:41,040
Now let's invite our female lead,

51
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:44,840
Chu Jingxi, to say a few words.

52
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:46,160
Let's give her a hand.

53
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:52,440
- Yeah! - Yeah!

54
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:01,560
Over the past few months,

55
00:03:02,440 --> 00:03:04,800
we've shared an incredible journey together.

56
00:03:05,880 --> 00:03:07,680
Behind every single shot,

57
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:10,440
was everyone's dedication and effort.

58
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:13,040
So,

59
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:16,760
I want to thank everyone, on and off camera.

60
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:20,320
Your professionalism and commitment

61
00:03:20,920 --> 00:03:22,680
brought "Have Fun"

62
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:23,720
to where it is today.

63
00:03:26,040 --> 00:03:29,960
I also want to thank my friends and family.

64
00:03:30,920 --> 00:03:33,760
You were there when I needed it most.

65
00:03:34,040 --> 00:03:35,480
Your support meant everything.

66
00:03:37,160 --> 00:03:39,760
Here's to "Have Fun".

67
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:42,960
Hope it resonates with viewers.

68
00:03:43,200 --> 00:03:44,400
- Yeah! - Yeah!

69
00:03:44,440 --> 00:03:46,440
- Well said! - Well said!

70
00:03:47,320 --> 00:03:48,640
- Big hit! - Definitely!

71
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:49,720
Great work.

72
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:51,560
Just doing our job.

73
00:03:51,640 --> 00:03:53,520
Once the show airs,

74
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:56,000
I'm sure you'll be back on top.

75
00:03:57,040 --> 00:03:58,320
I'll take your word for it.

76
00:03:59,320 --> 00:04:00,360
Drinks for everyone.

77
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:01,680
We're going all night.

78
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:05,080
- Yeah! - Yeah!

79
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:06,600
Great work, guys.

80
00:04:06,600 --> 00:04:07,520
- Mr. Wang. - Mr. Wang.

81
00:04:07,760 --> 00:04:08,680
Thank you for your support.

82
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:10,120
You're too kind, Mr. Song.

83
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:12,160
What's Yang up to?

84
00:04:12,480 --> 00:04:13,360
Said they're shooting some behind-the-scenes.

85
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:14,160
We're filming everything,

86
00:04:14,160 --> 00:04:16,360
so we can cut our own BTS later.

87
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:17,240
Stills and all.

88
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:18,000
Alright.

89
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:19,540
[Shocking! Actress Chu Jingxi allegedly involved in leaked private photos]

90
00:04:19,540 --> 00:04:20,740
[Reports claim Chu Jingxi was romantically involved with director Qi Siqin]

91
00:04:20,740 --> 00:04:22,400
[Cheating rumors surfaced before their wedding—now more details emerge]

92
00:04:22,440 --> 00:04:23,240
Look, look!

93
00:04:24,080 --> 00:04:25,840
- Who posted this? - This isn't...

94
00:04:27,320 --> 00:04:28,680
What's going on?

95
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:30,200
- No way. - Take a look.

96
00:04:30,200 --> 00:04:31,000
It's so clear.

97
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:31,800
- Exactly. - Is that really her?

98
00:04:32,320 --> 00:04:33,320
How far does this go?

99
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:34,840
Alright.

100
00:04:34,840 --> 00:04:36,320
Mr. Song, look.

101
00:04:36,320 --> 00:04:37,080
Sorry about this.

102
00:04:38,520 --> 00:04:39,480
I got it too.

103
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:40,400
Is everything okay?

104
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:42,920
Same thing?

105
00:04:44,200 --> 00:04:44,640
Director,

106
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:45,720
thank you for your hard work on this project.

107
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:46,840
Thank you. You as well.

108
00:04:46,840 --> 00:04:48,920
Hope we can work together again.

109
00:04:49,200 --> 00:04:50,200
Absolutely.

110
00:04:50,320 --> 00:04:50,960
Chu.

111
00:04:51,640 --> 00:04:52,360
What is it?

112
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:55,480
These photos, they're edited, right?

113
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:57,200
After all this work,

114
00:04:57,320 --> 00:04:59,800
we can't let it go to waste over this.

115
00:04:59,880 --> 00:05:01,360
Who did this?

116
00:05:02,080 --> 00:05:03,000
They're fake, right?

117
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:04,280
Look.

118
00:05:04,520 --> 00:05:05,760
Who's behind this?

119
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:07,840
I don't see any obvious edits.

120
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:08,920
Then they might be real.

121
00:05:11,960 --> 00:05:12,760
Chu.

122
00:05:17,280 --> 00:05:18,360
It's okay, Chu.

123
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:23,560
Chu.

124
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:23,880
Careful.

125
00:05:23,960 --> 00:05:24,680
Watch out!

126
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:27,520
Chu.

127
00:05:29,960 --> 00:05:32,440
This involves Ms. Chu's personal reputation.

128
00:05:32,520 --> 00:05:34,680
Please delete all false information and images.

129
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:35,480
Delete everything.

130
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:36,280
Thank you.

131
00:05:36,760 --> 00:05:38,040
Ai, make sure it's done.

132
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:38,920
Got it.

133
00:05:39,520 --> 00:05:40,200
Come on.

134
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:42,520
Delete everything you just received.

135
00:05:45,280 --> 00:05:46,080
Get PR on it now.

136
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:47,120
Track public sentiment.

137
00:05:47,200 --> 00:05:50,240
Tell the press it's misinformation or taken out of context.

138
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:53,240
Also line up some influencers and major accounts.

139
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:55,160
Push a few topics onto the trending list.

140
00:05:55,160 --> 00:05:56,440
Do not let this escalate.

141
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:58,160
Is that clear? Move.

142
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:01,400
Don't believe rumors or spread them.

143
00:06:01,400 --> 00:06:03,560
We will protect the production and Ms. Chu's reputation.

144
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:04,440
Everyone understand?

145
00:06:07,360 --> 00:06:08,160
Are you okay?

146
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:09,720
- The news just now... - You saw it?

147
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:11,280
Satisfying?

148
00:06:11,880 --> 00:06:13,120
Why did you follow me out here?

149
00:06:13,440 --> 00:06:14,440
To watch me fall apart?

150
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:18,680
I know this hurts.

151
00:06:20,200 --> 00:06:21,640
But no matter what happens,

152
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:23,120
I'm staying with you.

153
00:06:23,640 --> 00:06:24,800
We'll face it together.

154
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:25,720
We?

155
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:27,760
Who do you think you are,

156
00:06:27,760 --> 00:06:28,560
He Zheng?

157
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:30,200
Let me be clear.

158
00:06:30,280 --> 00:06:31,040
All along,

159
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:32,960
I never had real feelings for you.

160
00:06:32,960 --> 00:06:34,320
Don't flatter yourself.

161
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:37,480
Don't touch me!

162
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:39,480
I don't want to see you again!

163
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:41,120
There's nothing between us anymore!

164
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:42,400
Leave. Now.

165
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:44,360
Get out!

166
00:06:53,160 --> 00:06:54,760
If this is what you want,

167
00:06:59,300 --> 00:07:00,840
♪The story comes to an end♪

168
00:07:00,840 --> 00:07:01,680
then I'll go.

169
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:03,100
♪In a blink, it's late autumn♪

170
00:07:03,420 --> 00:07:05,020
♪After saying goodbye to you♪

171
00:07:05,100 --> 00:07:09,180
♪Smoke and drink can't drown the guilt♪

172
00:07:09,900 --> 00:07:11,780
♪Too young to know what sorrow was♪

173
00:07:11,780 --> 00:07:14,860
♪We once believed love would spare us pain♪

174
00:07:15,540 --> 00:07:18,860
♪Thank you for staying till the end, asking nothing♪

175
00:07:19,860 --> 00:07:23,220
♪I was childish, selfish in my freedom♪

176
00:07:23,220 --> 00:07:26,460
♪Letting you down again and again♪

177
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:31,840
♪I'll learn to face life on my own♪

178
00:07:31,840 --> 00:07:32,840
I'm sorry.

179
00:07:33,400 --> 00:07:34,200
He Zheng.

180
00:07:35,400 --> 00:07:36,200
I'm scared.

181
00:07:37,440 --> 00:07:39,440
I'm afraid this will drag you down.

182
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:44,800
I don't want you hurt because of me.

183
00:07:48,020 --> 00:07:49,370
♪Who else would♪

184
00:07:49,370 --> 00:07:50,620
♪See themselves in your eyes♪

185
00:07:50,860 --> 00:07:52,940
♪Hold you, kiss you, love you better than I did♪

186
00:07:52,940 --> 00:07:54,500
♪Take your hand in my place♪

187
00:07:54,500 --> 00:07:56,940
♪Watch the fireworks with you♪

188
00:07:56,940 --> 00:07:57,940
♪And let you be...♪

189
00:07:58,600 --> 00:07:59,400
He Zheng.

190
00:08:01,640 --> 00:08:02,440
Get in. Let's talk.

191
00:08:16,520 --> 00:08:17,240
Mr. Song.

192
00:08:20,200 --> 00:08:20,840
Speak.

193
00:08:21,760 --> 00:08:24,360
The message is spreading fast.

194
00:08:24,520 --> 00:08:25,760
Not just within the crew.

195
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:27,640
Our shareholders have seen it too.

196
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:29,000
Worse still,

197
00:08:29,320 --> 00:08:32,320
it's all over social media and news sites.

198
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:34,150
We need to act now,

199
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:37,550
or the damage to the company will be severe.

200
00:08:38,280 --> 00:08:39,720
What do you suggest we...

201
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:40,400
Track it.

202
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:43,120
Find the source.

203
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:46,480
I want the site and account IDs identified.

204
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:49,280
Find out who's behind this,

205
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:50,920
and what they're after.

206
00:08:51,400 --> 00:08:52,600
Prepare a crisis response.

207
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:55,840
If needed, we'll hold a press briefing.

208
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:57,080
Understood?

209
00:08:57,080 --> 00:08:58,480
Yes. I'll handle it.

210
00:09:03,920 --> 00:09:04,720
Thank you.

211
00:09:07,920 --> 00:09:09,320
This isn't for you.

212
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:10,520
What right do you have

213
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:13,680
to thank me?

214
00:09:14,640 --> 00:09:15,720
She's my girlfriend.

215
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:22,520
That's your claim.

216
00:09:23,520 --> 00:09:25,440
Until Chu Jingxi says it herself,

217
00:09:26,160 --> 00:09:27,360
that she loves you,

218
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:29,960
I'm not stepping aside.

219
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:34,480
Let me be clear.

220
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:37,200
I love her.

221
00:09:38,040 --> 00:09:39,160
I'm willing to wait,

222
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:42,680
until she understands how I feel,

223
00:09:43,280 --> 00:09:44,400
and give me a chance.

224
00:09:45,640 --> 00:09:46,560
This isn't over.

225
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:50,240
I won't back down.

226
00:09:50,560 --> 00:09:51,360
Fine.

227
00:09:52,280 --> 00:09:53,080
Good.

228
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:56,480
Remember what you said.

229
00:09:56,880 --> 00:09:58,280
But hear this too.

230
00:09:58,880 --> 00:10:00,040
Love isn't a war.

231
00:10:00,040 --> 00:10:01,400
There are no clear winners.

232
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:05,720
Her happiness comes first.

233
00:10:06,920 --> 00:10:09,920
I won't let her become collateral damage.

234
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:11,640
And I won't

235
00:10:12,400 --> 00:10:14,160
let her get hurt. Not even a little.

236
00:10:14,160 --> 00:10:14,960
I won't.

237
00:10:17,040 --> 00:10:18,840
Even if she chose you back then,

238
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:21,440
I still wouldn't quit.

239
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:30,280
Want a ride?

240
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:32,280
No.

241
00:10:33,440 --> 00:10:36,160
Thanks for being honest today, Mr. Song.

242
00:10:42,840 --> 00:10:43,640
Drive.

243
00:10:48,360 --> 00:10:49,720
This isn't for you.

244
00:10:49,760 --> 00:10:53,360
What right do you have to thank me?

245
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:54,760
Let me be clear.

246
00:10:56,640 --> 00:10:57,440
I love her.

247
00:10:58,320 --> 00:10:59,200
I'm willing to wait,

248
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:01,600
until she understands how I feel,

249
00:11:01,760 --> 00:11:02,840
and give me a chance.

250
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:18,400
Chu.

251
00:11:20,800 --> 00:11:22,440
I know this is really hard for you right now.

252
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:24,640
But I still want you to know,

253
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:26,360
you're not alone.

254
00:11:26,800 --> 00:11:28,560
We're all behind you.

255
00:11:28,560 --> 00:11:29,680
We'll face this together.

256
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:38,120
Alright.

257
00:11:38,680 --> 00:11:39,840
Get some rest.

258
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:41,280
I'll be right here.

259
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:43,400
If you need anything, just call me.

260
00:12:08,520 --> 00:12:09,880
I'm sorry, Yang.

261
00:12:10,680 --> 00:12:11,480
Take care.

262
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:28,880
Look at this.

263
00:12:28,880 --> 00:12:31,880
Isn't that Chu Jingxi,

264
00:12:31,880 --> 00:12:33,880
the one who's always acting all polished on camera?

265
00:12:33,920 --> 00:12:37,080
Yeah. She does have a good figure.

266
00:12:38,120 --> 00:12:41,520
[Chu Jingxi caught in photo leak]
She always puts on a cold front.

267
00:12:41,840 --> 00:12:42,680
Turns out she's not so pure after all.

268
00:12:44,680 --> 00:12:46,640
Doesn't matter. Still not getting near her.

269
00:12:47,320 --> 00:12:49,000
I wouldn't touch her anyway.

270
00:12:49,960 --> 00:12:51,400
Her fans

271
00:12:51,440 --> 00:12:52,760
are so naive.

272
00:12:53,560 --> 00:12:54,480
They really thought

273
00:12:54,560 --> 00:12:56,600
she was some kind of innocent goddess.

274
00:13:01,560 --> 00:13:03,000
Who the hell are you?

275
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:25,760
Chu.

276
00:13:28,400 --> 00:13:29,200
Chu?

277
00:13:30,360 --> 00:13:31,160
Chu?

278
00:13:31,160 --> 00:13:33,160
[Lighting Direction]

279
00:13:33,200 --> 00:13:34,000
Chu?

280
00:13:35,280 --> 00:13:36,080
Chu?

281
00:13:37,520 --> 00:13:38,320
Chu!

282
00:13:53,880 --> 00:13:54,840
Yang.

283
00:13:55,200 --> 00:13:56,000
He Zheng.

284
00:13:57,320 --> 00:13:57,960
Chu's gone.

285
00:13:57,960 --> 00:13:58,760
Get over here. Now.

286
00:14:00,960 --> 00:14:01,760
What did you say?

287
00:14:28,560 --> 00:14:31,520
